Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我并不想拿起利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:13.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.83,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不流泪 不畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}燃烧 燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你告诉我 我错过了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.76,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}仍在浓雾中彷徨
